# ============================================================
# BIU Smart App — API Test Suite
# VS Code REST Client extension format
# Run order: Auth first → copy tokens → run the rest
#
# Seed phone numbers:
#   Staff   → +998901111001 / +998901111002 / +998901111003
#   Student → +998902222001 / +998902222002 / +998902222003
#   Admin   → +998900000001
#   Password (all): 1234
# ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

# After running auth requests paste the JWT values below:
@STAFF_TOKEN   = REPLACE_WITH_STAFF_TOKEN
@STUDENT_TOKEN = REPLACE_WITH_STUDENT_TOKEN
@ADMIN_TOKEN   = REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_TOKEN


# ===========================================================
### 1. AUTH TESTS
# ===========================================================

### 1-1. Staff login — expect 200, token in response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+998901111001",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 1-2. Wrong password — expect 400, Uzbek error message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+998901111001",
  "password": "wrongpass"
}

###

### 1-3. Student login — expect 200, token in response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+998902222001",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 1-4. Admin login — expect 200, token in response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+998900000001",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 1-5. Missing phone field — expect 400, validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 1-6. Short password (< 4 chars) — expect 400, validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+998901111001",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### 1-7. Non-existent phone — expect 400/404, user not found
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+998909999999",
  "password": "1234"
}

###


# ===========================================================
### 2. WORK TESTS  (requires STAFF_TOKEN)
# ===========================================================

### 2-1. Get active log — expect 200 (null if not checked in yet)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/work/active
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 2-2. Check in to Bino 1 (correct GPS) — expect 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "buildingId": 1,
  "lat": 39.7747,
  "lon": 64.4286
}

###

### 2-3. Double check-in (same building) — expect 400, "allaqachon belgilangansiz"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "buildingId": 1,
  "lat": 39.7747,
  "lon": 64.4286
}

###

### 2-4. Check in with wrong GPS (Toshkent) — expect 400, "Siz binoda emassiz"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "buildingId": 1,
  "lat": 41.2995,
  "lon": 69.2401
}

###

### 2-5. Get today session — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/work/today
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 2-6. Check out (correct GPS) — expect 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "lat": 39.7747,
  "lon": 64.4286
}

###

### 2-7. Get weekly report — expect 200, array of sessions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/work/week
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 2-8. Get monthly report — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/work/month?year=2025&month=4
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 2-9. No token — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/work/today

###


# ===========================================================
### 3. STAFF TESTS  (requires STAFF_TOKEN)
# ===========================================================

### 3-1. Get staff profile — expect 200, profile object
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 3-2. Get work stats — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/work-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 3-3. Get vacation list — expect 200, empty array initially
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/vacations
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 3-4. Request vacation — expect 200/201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/vacations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "type": "yillik",
  "start_date": "2025-05-01",
  "end_date": "2025-05-10",
  "reason": "Yillik ta'til"
}

###

### 3-5. Invalid vacation type — expect 400, validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/vacations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "type": "invalid_type",
  "start_date": "2025-05-01",
  "end_date": "2025-05-10"
}

###

### 3-6. Get rewards list — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/rewards
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 3-7. Student trying staff endpoint — expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/staff/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###


# ===========================================================
### 4. STUDENT TESTS  (requires STUDENT_TOKEN)
# ===========================================================

### 4-1. Get student profile — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 4-2. Get today schedule (IT-22-1) — expect 200, lesson list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/schedule/today
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 4-3. Get week schedule — expect 200, grouped by day
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/schedule?week=0
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 4-4. Get attendance summary — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/attendance/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 4-5. Get grades — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/grades
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 4-6. Get assignments — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 4-7. QR check-in with invalid token — expect 400, "QR kod topilmadi"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/student/attendance/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

{
  "token": "invalid-token-123",
  "lat": 39.7747,
  "lon": 64.4286
}

###

### 4-8. Staff trying student endpoint — expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/student/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###


# ===========================================================
### 5. NOTIFICATIONS TESTS
# ===========================================================

### 5-1. Get notifications (staff) — expect 200, array
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 5-2. Get notifications (student) — expect 200, array
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 5-3. Mark all read — expect 200
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 5-4. No token — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications

###


# ===========================================================
### 6. REPORTS TESTS  (requires STAFF_TOKEN)
# ===========================================================

### 6-1. Daily report — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 6-2. Weekly report without from param — expect 200, auto Monday (FIX 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 6-2b. Weekly report with explicit from — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/weekly?from=2026-04-21
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 6-3. Monthly report — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/monthly?year=2025&month=4
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###


# ===========================================================
### 7. ADMIN TESTS  (requires ADMIN_TOKEN)
# ===========================================================

### 7-1. Get all staff — expect 200, array
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/staff
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

###

### 7-2. Get active-now staff — expect 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/staff/active-now
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

###

### 7-3. Get overview — expect 200, stats object
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

###

### 7-4. Generate QR for schedule id 1 — expect 200, token string
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/qr/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "scheduleId": 1
}

###

### 7-5. Send broadcast notification — expect 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/notify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "userIds": [],
  "type": "tizim",
  "title": "Test xabar",
  "body": "Bu test xabarnomasi"
}

###

### 7-6. Invalid notification type — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/notify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "userIds": [],
  "type": "invalid_type",
  "title": "Test",
  "body": "Test"
}

###

### 7-7. Student using admin endpoint — expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

###

### 7-8. Staff using admin endpoint — expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 7-9. No token on admin route — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/overview

###


# ===========================================================
### 8. FIX TESTS — same-day re-checkin & weekly report
# ===========================================================

### 8-1. Reset today session (after checkout) — expect 200 (FIX 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/reset-session
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 8-2. Re-checkin same day after reset — expect 200 (FIX 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "buildingId": 2,
  "lat": 39.740624,
  "lon": 64.432623
}

###

### 8-3. Today shows multiple logs — expect 200, logs array length > 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/work/today
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###

### 8-4. Checkout from Bino 2 — expect 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

{
  "lat": 39.740624,
  "lon": 64.432623
}

###

### 8-5. Reset when active log exists — expect 400 (FIX 1 guard)
# First checkin to make active log, then try reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/work/reset-session
Authorization: Bearer {{STAFF_TOKEN}}

###


# ===========================================================
# EXPECTED RESULTS SUMMARY
# ===========================================================
# 1-1  Staff login success        → 200, { token, user }
# 1-2  Wrong password             → 400, Uzbek error message
# 1-3  Student login success      → 200, { token, user }
# 1-4  Admin login success        → 200, { token, user }
# 1-5  Missing phone              → 400, validation error
# 1-6  Short password             → 400, min 4 chars
# 1-7  Non-existent user          → 400/404
# 2-2  Check-in correct GPS       → 200, log entry created
# 2-3  Double check-in            → 400, "allaqachon belgilangansiz"
# 2-4  Wrong GPS check-in         → 400, "Siz binoda emassiz"
# 2-9  No token (work)            → 401
# 3-5  Invalid vacation type      → 400
# 3-7  Student → staff endpoint   → 403
# 4-7  Invalid QR token           → 400, "QR kod topilmadi"
# 4-8  Staff → student endpoint   → 403
# 5-4  No token (notifications)   → 401
# 7-7  Student → admin endpoint   → 403
# 7-8  Staff → admin endpoint     → 403
# 7-9  No token (admin)           → 401
# 8-1  Reset session              → 200, "Sessiya qayta faollashtirildi"
# 8-2  Re-checkin same day        → 200, log entry created
# 8-3  Today shows multiple logs  → 200, logs.length >= 2
# 8-4  Checkout Bino 2            → 200
# 8-5  Reset with active log      → 400, "aktiv kirish mavjud"
# 6-2  Weekly no param            → 200, auto Monday used
# 6-2b Weekly with from param     → 200
